        "state": "engineered",
        "edbb": {
          "role": "trading",
          "intro": "A cheap medium-pad trade fit that keeps a small shield. Initial is buy-only; A-rated is the trade baseline; Engineered maximises laden range and basic survivability.",
          "callout": {
            "label": "Cargo plus a small shield",
            "text": "Fill the optionals with cargo but keep one class-4 slot for a bi-weave shield — the Type-6 is lightly built, and even a small shield greatly improves your odds against an interdiction while you learn the routes."
          },
          "notes": {
            "TinyHardpoint1": "One shield booster is the cheapest large multiplier on a small bi-weave; Heavy Duty maximises its raw MJ.",
            "TinyHardpoint2": "Optional / low-priority — Ammo Capacity adds rounds. Point Defence shoots down incoming missiles and torpedoes.",
            "TinyHardpoint3": "Optional / low-priority — Ammo Capacity adds heat-sink charges. Dumps heat for silent running and Thermal-Vent resets.",
            "PowerPlant": "Size-3 plant powers the shield, booster and modules; Low Emissions cuts heat and signature to make you harder to find.",
            "MainEngines": "A-rate then Dirty Drives — raw speed is your main escape tool, since the hull cannot out-fight anything.",
            "FrameShiftDrive": "A-rate FIRST — the Type-6's strong laden range is its whole value; Increased Range + Mass Manager pushes it furthest.",
            "LifeSupport": "D-rate to save mass; Lightweight trims more — life support has no experimental effect.",
            "PowerDistributor": "A-rate for boost recharge; Engine Focused biases ENG so you can boost clear of an interdiction.",
            "Radar": "Drop to D and go Lightweight; a trader needs no sensor range, so save the mass for range.",
            "FuelTank": "Stock C tank sized to the laden jump range; fuel capacity is fixed and cannot be engineered.",
            "Slot01_Size5": "Optional — Expanded Capacity adds cargo space; worth it for dedicated haulers. Holds cargo.",
            "Slot02_Size5": "Optional — Expanded Capacity adds cargo space; worth it for dedicated haulers. Holds cargo.",
            "Slot03_Size4": "One size-4 slot spent on a bi-weave; it regenerates fast and Reinforced + Fast Charge keep you alive long enough to flee.",
            "Slot04_Size4": "Optional — Expanded Capacity adds cargo space; worth it for dedicated haulers. Holds cargo.",
            "Slot05_Size3": "Optional — Expanded Capacity adds cargo space; worth it for dedicated haulers. Holds cargo.",
            "Slot06_Size2": "Optional — Expanded Capacity adds cargo space; worth it for dedicated haulers. Holds cargo.",
            "Slot07_Size2": "Optional / low-priority — Specialised cuts the cell bank's heat and power spike. Burst shield healing for emergencies.",
            "Slot08_Size1": "Optional / low-priority — Expanded Probe Scanning widens probe coverage. Maps planets for exploration data."
